&lt;P&gt;They've just done exactly the same as they did with the merchants in PoK that time where folks could buy items at reduced prices.&amp;nbsp; Instead of just accepting they **HALFLING**ed up &amp;amp; removing the merchants quickly, they left them up far too long and then spent ages rolling back *anybody* even remotely connected to the merchants.&amp;nbsp; People lost items / xp with no idea why.&amp;nbsp; I never saw a good explanation for why they had to do that to everyone.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
