&lt;P&gt;If they just considered these things from the players point of view &amp;amp; tried to make sure the changes are fair on those who have been affected they'd be getting a lot less grief on the forums and players wouldn't have such a negative view of the company.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Hell, they could post the question on the forums first saying, "we **HALFLING**ed up, it needs correcting and the options are these.&amp;nbsp; Which would you prefer we do?".&amp;nbsp; Ok, it takes a little more planning but all of a sudden you're working with the community instead of fighting them off after every patch.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
